nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/lug/services/mirrors</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#20-6","id":"1143485","time":"2016-3-21 02:05","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">板砖加身</span> 说: 换中科大的源：https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/lug/services/mirrors</q></div>是这个：<a href=\"https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/ubuntu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/ubuntu</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/21/102199.jpg","floor":"#20-7","id":"1143492","time":"2016-3-21 02:23","userId":"zainer","userName":"阿布拉其阿亚尔阿肯尔","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fantasy</span> 说: 是这个：https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/ubuntu</q></div>换了 错误代码倒是没了 就是下载应用一直停在更新缓存"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/26/12630.jpg","floor":"#20-8","id":"1143493","time":"2016-3-21 02:23","userId":"gongt","userName":"魂魄妖梦","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fantasy</span> 说: 是这个：https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/ubuntu</q></div>我从中科大源下载软件很大几率hash不符。。现在我直接改host把他墙了（。<br>下个软件都要开代理去国外下。。啧啧。。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#20-9","id":"1143494","time":"2016-3-21 02:25","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fantasy</span> 说: 是这个：https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/ubuntu</q></div>其实 sed -i s@cn.archive.ubuntu.com@mirrors.ustc.edu.cn@g /etc/apt/sources.list  好了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#20-10","id":"1143495","time":"2016-3-21 02:26","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">魂魄妖梦</span> 说: 我从中科大源下载软件很大几率hash不符。。现在我直接改ho